social_media_scraper.py

Fetch a webpage via urllib and extract basic metadata (title + description).

Security considerations:
- Only allows http/https URLs.
- Blocks requests to localhost, loopback, link-local, and private IP ranges to reduce SSRF risk.
- Uses a certifi-backed SSL context for HTTPS.
- Limits response size and enforces timeouts.
- Avoids decompressing content (no automatic gzip decoding) and does best-effort charset handling.
