Fetches a remote webpage via urllib and extracts basic metadata (title and description).
Designed to be safe-by-default:
- HTTPS verification uses certifi CA bundle.
- Only http/https URLs are allowed.
- Prevents SSRF to localhost/private/link-local/multicast/reserved IPs.
- Limits redirects, response size, and timeouts.
- Parses HTML without executing scripts.
